on a regular basis.

272
00:10:41,737 --> 00:10:42,904
So you just chalk it up
to coincidence

273
00:10:42,971 --> 00:10:45,273
that the six leaders
of this demonstration,

274
00:10:45,324 --> 00:10:48,159
against
your company's policies,

275
