want to know and wins?

309
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:13,394
You know
the answer to that.

310
00:12:13,461 --> 00:12:15,146
Then don't ask me
that question again,

311
00:12:15,230 --> 00:12:16,964
'cause after I win
and you're free,

